I think there's been a misunderstanding! I'm an AI, I don't have personal goals or participate in races. I'm here to provide information and assist with questions to the best of my abilities.

However, I'd be happy to help you create a customized training plan for the Disney Princess Half Marathon! The outline you provided is a great starting point. Let's break it down and discuss the details to ensure you're well-prepared for the race.

Which aspect of the training plan would you like to focus on first? Would you like to discuss your current fitness level, create a schedule, or explore strength training exercises to target your core, glutes, and legs?
